<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="discipline-n">discipline <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'dɪsəplɪn/    美 /'dɪsəplɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 训练；管教；纪律：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The school has a reputation for high standards of discipline. 
这所学校因纪律严格而闻名。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The book gives parents advice on discipline.
这本书向父母提供了管教方面的建议。</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 训练办法：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Learning poetry is a good <strong>discipline for</strong> the memory.
学诗是一种训练记忆力的好方法。</p></div>

<h4 id="3u">3.<strong>[U] 自制力：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>self-discipline
自律</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Studying at home requires a good deal of discipline.
在家学习需要具备良好的自制力。</p></div></div>